snippet.title: Dark Pact launch trailer
snippet.description:
Manipulate enemy positioning and use the environment to your advantage. Utilize clever combos to defeat overwhelming odds in this tactical turn-based strategy game with a focus on creativity rather than number crunching.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2498740/Dark_Pact/
